sentences.en: Descriptions of the pieces have been logged on computer by the Art Loss Register.
sentences.cn: 艺术品失窃登记处已经将这些艺术品的描述信息输入到计算机里。

sentences.en: Details of the crime are then logged in the computer.
sentences.cn: 随后会将罪案的详细情况录入到计算机里。

sentences.en: He logged the ship's speed at 10 knots.
sentences.cn: 他在航海日志之中记下船速每小时十海里.

sentences.en: My IP address is dynamic. How do I stay logged in?
sentences.cn: 我的IP是动态的, 如何保持登陆状态?

sentences.en: Not logged in. Your password is being rejected, contact the server administrator.
sentences.cn: 不能登录. 你的密码被拒绝, 请联系服务器管理员.

sentences.en: Redirect local drives when logged on to the remote computer.
sentences.cn: 登录到远程计算机时重定向本地驱动器.

sentences.en: The pilot had logged over 200 hours in the air.
sentences.cn: 这个飞行员的飞行记录在200小时以上.

sentences.en: They asked the pilot how many hours he had logged.
sentences.cn: 他们问那飞行员累积了多少飞行时数.

sentences.en: They logged the timber into 7 - foot length.
sentences.cn: 他们把那根木材锯成七英尺长.

sentences.en: They logged up the ship's position regularly.
sentences.cn: 他们定时把船的方位记入航海日志.

sentences.en: This media contains an unknown data format and cannot be logged.
sentences.cn: 该媒体包含未知数据格式,无法记录.

sentences.en: This media contains user data and cannot be logged.
sentences.cn: 该媒体包含用户数据,无法记录.

sentences.en: We have logged up a remarkable series of gains in technical innovation.
sentences.cn: 我们已在技术革新方面取得一系列可观的成就.

sentences.en: Within half an hour we had logged every car.
sentences.cn: 在半个小时内,我们把每一辆车都作了登记.

sentences.en: You are logged in. To modify your account settings, click here.
sentences.cn: 你是登录修改你的帐户设置, 请点击这里.
